{"tid":1657323,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"琴晚我係藍絲老母面前倒咗碗湯","createTime":"2019-10-16T04:43:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T07:24:20.000Z","uid":251052,"like":23,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3d2f94a6b7d1e6ffb6956d25ede4513b1ee943c9","tid":1657323,"uid":251052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T04:43:41.000Z","msg":"話說頭先我打緊MHWI個陣<br />\n我老母無端端捧碗湯入黎叫我飲左佢<br />\n咁打緊金獅子又點分神飲湯 咁咪話一陣飲<br />\n點知我老母5分鐘入黎煩我一次<br />\n最後我頂唔撚順問佢 點解要飲湯牙<br />\n佢話 湯有營養<br />\n我話 點解有營養 你可唔可以解釋下<br />\n佢當然解釋唔到<br />\n然後我就食住上 我話 你自己都解釋唔到 因為你從來唔會思考 你甚至懶得思考 你只會遵從上一輩教你既知識<br />\n你抗拒新事物 你只會認為自己做咗咁多年既野一定係啱<br />\n你更加唔會思考班後生仔點解要出黎抗爭 <br />\n你連思考都懶 睇新聞都要睇果d為你設定埋立場既tvb <br />\n我唔會再跟你果套<br />\n呢碗湯 我唔會飲<br />\n講完我就倒咗碗湯"},{"pid":"73a12ce96c2d8dfa941cead697ad886423d31baf","tid":1657323,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T04:44:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zBif5mg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzBif5mg.jpg&h=44757529&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"c0e51942f658ce6a8e64a53a218f60b149794689","tid":1657323,"uid":161541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T04:44:48.000Z","msg":"Ching ho ball"},{"pid":"9609b3443e67f808dbb4b936abb7b6e0d7bb4d94","tid":1657323,"uid":166616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T04:46:13.000Z","msg":"好波"},{"pid":"d6de6df405bec549c392afe1a58e3e68f721c6a9","tid":1657323,"uid":3454,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T04:47:56.000Z","msg":"無左眼濕濕扮委屈個段<br />\n負皮"},{"pid":"6ddd7dee15cc345fbfab3748ed6b184e2517a909","tid":1657323,"uid":107611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T04:48:41.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"65b50d883c82bb7cb8bb92f90cd5b0d0be52834c","tid":1657323,"uid":130121,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T04:50:29.000Z","msg":"好快有藍屍group cap圖 廣傳<img src=\"/assets/fac